{"tid":850114,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全球災難危機（Global catastrophic risk）","createTime":"2018-10-06T08:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T09:12:54.000Z","uid":26429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41e2e9af81e18cb03f83002c6052f157a3a89db6","tid":850114,"uid":26429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"全球災難危機（Global catastrophic risk）是一個概念，假設人類於未來將遭逢全球災難性的事件，導致現代文明毀滅、倒退或衰落，又稱為世界末日。<br />\n<br />\n來自太空的災難:<br />\n巨大的星體撞擊<br />\n近距離的超新星爆發<br />\n外星人入侵<br />\n<br />\n來自地球本身的災難:<br />\n全球性瘟疫<br />\n超級火山爆發<br />\n氣候變化<br />\n地磁消失或翻轉<br />\n<br />\n來自人類的災難:<br />\n核戰爭<br />\n不可逆轉的氣候變化<br />\n不可逆轉的生態災變<br />\n黃金週(中國)"},{"pid":"aaf840ba38447a574cd72c1c09b42d7eeeffa38d","tid":850114,"uid":44163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tse3.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.euKMhobdooeeBt1oXot-6AHaKQ&amp;pid=15.1221160\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftse3.mm.bing.net%2Fth%3Fid%3DOIP.euKMhobdooeeBt1oXot-6AHaKQ%26pid%3D15.1221160&h=edb72bdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddf16d1a3fdfbdca317926a421b52682787cbb98","tid":850114,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaf840ba38447a574cd72c1c09b42d7eeeffa38d","tid":850114,"uid":44163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tse3.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.euKMhobdooeeBt1oXot-6AHaKQ&amp;pid=15.1221160\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftse3.mm.bing.net%2Fth%3Fid%3DOIP.euKMhobdooeeBt1oXot-6AHaKQ%26pid%3D15.1221160&h=edb72bdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"佢食晒d野未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e141fe1291b6479828e9d4ae0a1d98f7e8cccc7","tid":850114,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e2e9af81e18cb03f83002c6052f157a3a89db6","tid":850114,"uid":26429,"like":0,